                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote scope="major" script="nasta_liq" medium="ink">
                        Copied in stylish <material>black</material> nasta‘līq with shikastah ligratures by <persName key="person_f1839" role="scr" change="#role-assignment">Kāshī Nath</persName>.<lb/>
